Activated Ability; Re-use time 30 Minutes<br>
Cost: 5<br>
This is an irresistable ability which lowers fire and cold resists by 50. This ability stacks with the mala line of spells<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><b><i>Quote:</i></b><hr>   <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b>   Summon the Heroes</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
Activated Ability; Re-use time 14 Minutes<br>
Cost: 9<br>
This ability summons all players in your party to your location, regardless if they are in zone or not.<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><b><i>Quote:</i></b><hr>   <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b>   Elemental Warding</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
Activated Ability; Re-use time 42 minutes first level, 48 minutes second level, 60 minutes third level.<br>
Cost: 3 per level (3 levels)<br>
At first level, this is a self-only raise fire and cold resist by 75. At second level this becomes a group ability, at the cost of raising the re-use time by 6 minutes. At third level with becomes the equivilent of a Mass Group Buff, at the cost of raising the re-use time by an additional 12 minutes. This ability stacks with other increase-resist spells. The duration is 42 minutes.<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><b><i>Quote:</i></b><hr>   <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b>   Mystical Orb of Transvergance</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
Activated Ability; Re-use time 1 hour 12 minutes<br>
Cost: 15<br>
This summons an Mystical Orb of Transvergance to the magicians current location. When this orb is clicked on by a non-melee character, it casts Modulate with a casting time similar to the Shaman's Cannibalize spell. This orb has unlimited charges and lasts for 5 minutes. Using this ability drains all the magicians mana.<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
<br>
I updated these based on your opinions. Bane of Elements now has a lower re-use time and would stack with mala type spells, at the cost of reducing the ammount of resistances it lowers. Summon the Heroes has a lower re-use time. Elemental Warding now is an activated ability that starts as a self-buff, then becomes a group buff, and finally a Mass Group Buff. Mystical Orb of Transvergance now costs 12 instead of 9, and drains all the magicians mana. <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/uarchangyl.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Archangyl</A> at: 8/23/02 1:40:53 am<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/uiwanthewicca.showPublicProfile?language=EN>IwanTheWicca</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Magician</span><br>  Posts: 87<br> <font color=#333333>(8/22/02 3:35:27 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm32.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=306.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> <img src="http://www.ezboard.com/images/posticons/pi_smile.gif" align=absmiddle>  Nice ideas</span><hr size=1> Bane of Elements:<br>
<br>
I'd rather see an instant reuse -50 FR/CR debuff That way Malosini is still a viable spell. Unless they both stack which is an idea I'm not too keen on.<br>
<br>
<br>
Summon Heroes:<br>
<br>
Nice idea for an inverse translocate.<br>
<br>
<br>
Elemental Warding:<br>
<br>
I doubt many magicians would use this. I'd prefer it to be a +10/level for 3 levels with a much higher AA point cost.<br>
<br>
<br>
Orb of Mystical Transvergence:<br>
<br>
I assume this is an unlimited charge Level 44 mod rod. Only the magician would have any interest in using this since the level 56 rod is far better to use.<br>
<br>
Still, some nice ideas. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#dcdeed><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/umagetlow.showPublicProfile?language=EN>magetlow</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Magician</span><br>  Posts: 7<br> <font color=#333333>(8/22/02 5:40:14 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm32.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=306.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> <img src="http://www.ezboard.com/images/posticons/pi_smile.gif" align=absmiddle>  Re: Nice ideas</span><hr size=1> i have an idea for a new aa rather in class or arch.<br>
we all know we got screwed with aa so this would balance it out. - pet crits-passive- 3 lvl's just like any melee % or even a little less. we need something to help us and i can see this doing alot. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/usambus.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Sambus</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Elementalist</span><br>  Posts: 101<br> <font color=#333333>(8/22/02 5:40:37 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm32.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=306.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.shiftclick.net/eq/sigs/60x60tinker.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> <img src="http://www.ezboard.com/images/posticons/pi_smile.gif" align=absmiddle>  Re: Nice ideas</span><hr size=1> I like Bane of Elements.  Reuse time is too high though - it's nice, but it's more like Cann5 nice, not Manaburn nice.<br>
<br>
Group CoH is nifty but I think its use would be rather limited.  With a recast time that long it's not very useful for CoH'ing raid groups faster, and you'd not want to use it in a pull situation, so there's not much use left that I can think of.<br>
<br>
Elemental Warding would be more effective if it gave a greater boost to resists, though honestly are resists really a problem for a lot of people anymore?  Considering ae bard resist songs, resist buffs (seasons, grm, etc), standard resists on most Velious+ items, and various resist AA abilities (both in general and in the air elemental form class skill), resists aren't as big an issue as they used to be, in my opinion.<br>
<br>
Orb is creative, but if I understand it right, you're basically summoning a manastone that an entire raid can have access to.  As cool as it would look to have all your casters crowded around a glowing orb, it's probably just a little too powerful <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p><font face="Verdana">
<b><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=24658" target=_blank>Sambus Veneficus</a></b><br> Arch Mage of Ak'anon<br> Mithaniel Marr Server</font><br><br></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#dcdeed><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/uznailvh.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Znail vh</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Elementalist</span><br>  Posts: 151<br> <font color=#333333>(8/22/02 7:43:53 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm32.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=306.topic&index=4>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> <img src="http://www.ezboard.com/images/posticons/pi_smile.gif" align=absmiddle>  Re: Nice ideas</span><hr size=1> If the orb is too powerful, then the reuse can be longer perhaps. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/ukathodos.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Kathodos</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Magician</span><br>  Posts: 91<br> <font color=#333333>(8/23/02 7:07:06 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm32.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=306.topic&index=5>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.battle.net/war3/images/human/units/animations/waterelement.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> <img src="http://www.ezboard.com/images/posticons/pi_lightbulb.gif" align=absmiddle>  Re: Some AA Ideas...</span><hr size=1> <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b>  Bane of the Elements</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> (BoE):<br>
Make this 35 instead of 50, and I actually don't see too many issues with this.<br>
<br>
BoE + Mala = 70 from Fire/Cold resists.<br>
BoE + Malo = 80 from Fire/Cold resists.<br>
